- Using ARESITOS as part of paid training courses or certifications

PERMITTED USES (NON-COMMERCIAL ONLY):
- Personal cybersecurity education and learning
- Academic research and educational institutions (non-profit)
- Open source community projects and contributions
- Personal security testing on own systems or with explicit authorization
- Sharing knowledge and improvements with the cybersecurity community

